    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated to meet rigorous standards of performance and aesthetic appeal. Meticulously maintained and demonstrating superior mechanical integrity, it offers a refined driving experience for the discerning professional. This acquisition represents a premier balance of sophisticated engineering and enduring value.",
      "price": 36400.0,
