    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in wonderful shape, drives super smoothly, and has been really well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend adventure, this car is ready to go and won't let you down! I'd love for it to go to a new home where it'll be appreciated just as much as I've enjoyed it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3, featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 paired with a traditional 6-speed manual transmission. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies to deliver exceptional throttle response up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and a Variable M Differential Lock for superior lateral dynamics. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the internal reciprocating assembly remains robust. While exhibiting minor aesthetic wear consistent with enthusiast use, the structural integrity and drivetrain performance remain uncompromising. A visceral, analog driving experience for the discerning pilot.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
